Michael C. Maronna https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_C._Maronna 0 Michael C. Maronna (born September 27, 1977) is an American actor who has appeared in several television programs and films. He is best known for his role as "Big Pete" on the TV show The Adventures of Pete Pete.
